&lt;h1 class="relative group">Summary of The Odyssey
&lt;div id="summary-of-the-odyssey" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#summary-of-the-odyssey" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
