&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Ir was ritten by &lt;strong>Homer&lt;/strong>, the same poet who wrote &lt;em>The Iliad&lt;/em>. It was composed around &lt;strong>8th century BCE&lt;/strong> in ancient Greece.&lt;br>
It is an &lt;strong>epic poem&lt;/strong> with &lt;strong>24 books&lt;/strong> (sections), written in &lt;strong>dactylic hexameter&lt;/strong>, Contains &lt;strong>over 12,000 lines&lt;/strong> of poetry.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;em>The Odyssey&lt;/em> is about &lt;strong>human resilience, wisdom, and the longing for home&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>